      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-stp-prn-mrk-uno    not  = spaces
                     go to prn-rou-pri-300.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se primo passaggio                              *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
